{"tid":2032363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望今日係我地香港人嘅新開始","createTime":"2020-05-24T04:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T04:44:30.000Z","uid":86453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef1a9eea956b405bf38bc45e10c410cf1494e9c","tid":2032363,"uid":86453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"好多post大家心情都好沉重 <br />\n係到好想大家懷住一個有希望嘅心出去！<br />\n因為種種原因 我好耐都無出去發夢<br />\n但今日無論如何我都會出去 <br />\n笑9我送頭又好 無腦又好<br />\n但我想講今日都唔出 唔好係以後失去自由自黎喊<br />\n仲記唔記得6月個陣 「人多就安全」呢句說話<br />\n雖然依加人多唔一定安全<br />\n但人少就一定唔安全<br />\n多你一個差好遠 一齊互相保護<br />\n<br />\n最後！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝大家凱旋回歸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb40080baf84b76b13a3a08e34fa8aa143b7e5d3","tid":2032363,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc288103178d34f0ceccd6a2d22abdd40684495","tid":2032363,"uid":130076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a909d7d0e52aeebc199bec4e2402b28589938130","tid":2032363,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"「524」大遊行全攻略！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2032373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2032373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}